Text: Thank you very much -inspiron- another great upload!

This is by far the best ASOT in months, hands down. The only horrible track is "Denis Kenzo feat. Sveta B. - Lullaby Lonely (Progressive Mix)." I'm excited that he pumped up this episode to tracks over 138bpm to get ready for ASOT 600 all around the world. It's going to be EPIC!
rhodyvik I share your enthusiasm, can't wait to hear this one out :). Too bad hes not coming anywhere near Balkan for his tour.
